<![CDATA[<p class="MsoNormal" style=""><font face="arial">Hi {!Contact.FirstName},<br></font><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><br>We have been attempting to contact you regarding the outstanding payment for your business insurance. Unfortunately, as we have not heard from you, </span><b style="font-size: 12pt;">the outstanding balance has been referred over to debt collection</b><span style="font-size: 12pt;">.<br></span><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><br>The</span><b style="font-size: 12pt;"> debt collection agency (Oriel Collections) will reach out to you in the coming days to discuss the next steps with you</b><span style="font-size: 12pt;">. Please contact them on </span><b style="font-size: 12pt;">01242 508639</b><span style="font-size: 12pt;"> with any queries.<br></span><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><br>Kind regards,<br></span><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><br>{!User.FirstName}<br></span><span style="font-size: 12pt;">Customer Accounts Team<br></span><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><br>E: customersupport@kingsbridge.co.uk<br></span><span style="font-size: 12pt;">T: 01242 808 740</span></p>]]></td>
